Definition: in an unpardonable manner or to an unpardonable degree
Example: he was inexcusably cruel to his wife
Synonyms: excusably, adj, all, inexcusable, unpardonably, pardonably, unpardonable, unforgivably, forgivably, unforgivable, in, an, manner, or, to, degree, he, was, cruel, his, wife
Category: adv.all
